item.title: Help 6 errors when adding a command
item.dc:creator: @mudger47 mudger47
item.description:
@mudger47 wrote:

[quote=“Sir Jay, post:2, topic:376863”]You need to declare your variables and make sure you are calling them from the correct file\path.

Tip: if you are using Delta its sM and not sendMessage. and its toY and toX I think, but that is only if you are using DELTAAAAA[/quote]

thanks that was the problem
